		"name": "RentNest Backend API",
		"description": "## Introduction\n\n**RentNest** is a secure RESTful API for a property rental platform where landlords can list properties, tenants can browse and request rentals, and payments are processed securely using Stripe.\n\nThe API follows REST principles, JWT authentication, role-based authorization, and consistent response structures.\n\n**Base URL**\n\n``` http\nhttp://localhost:5000/api\n\n ```\n\n**Production**\n\n```\nhttps://rentnest-seven.vercel.app/api\n\n ```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "55043461",
		"_collection_link": "https://odvutkabbo-4812512.postman.co/workspace/b7a54be5-084d-4aac-8394-531758099c4d/collection/55043461-cf30ffa0-96f2-44d5-a2cc-3047ba9bd05a?action=share&source=collection_link&creator=55043461"
